      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="dna" size={22} /></div>
        <h4>Adaptive Immunity</h4>
        <p>Supports T-cell maturation and differentiation, B-cell antibody production, and the resolution phase of inflammation. Adequate vitamin C status accelerates the transition from active immune response to tissue repair.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="flask" size={22} /></div>
        <h4>Antioxidant Protection</h4>
        <p>As the primary water-soluble antioxidant, vitamin C neutralizes reactive oxygen species (ROS) generated during immune battles. This protects immune cells from self-inflicted oxidative damage during inflammatory responses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="heart" size={22} /></div>
